146
00:07:51,246 --> 00:07:52,246
Dein

147
00:07:52,623 --> 00:07:54,499
Ihr Büro.

148
00:07:54,958 --> 00:07:56,501
Nun ja, äh...

149
00:07:57,294 --> 00:07:58,147
